snippet.title: Super Blockbuster | Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Super Blockbuster is our love letter to the action puzzle games of our youth. Solve tricky puzzles and take on a diverse cast of enemies, all in gorgeous pixel art inspired by the golden age of 2D puzzle games.

Play the demo and wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2830100/Super_Blockbuster/
Game Intro: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=46b2LYt0cUE
